Name: Pressured
About the game: Pressured is a unique and intense number puzzler. Hit your targets to unlock pieces of the dark story, all told via the poetry of Nicholas Gordon. You'll need a combination of quick thinking and sharp reflexes if you don't want to succumb to the pressure.
